::Magmatron::

    "The Judge, well me, was a Quientession. He would dispense his kind of 
Justice, and he did to many a Transformer," Magmatron began. "He would put 
the Transformer on trial, and then after the trial was done, he would give 
the vertic. Guilty or Innocent, either way it ment no difference to me. The 
Trasformer would die at the hands of the Sharkticons, which would be why I 
had chosen CyberShark as one of my warriors.
    "Hot Rod and Kup were to be on trial next, this was during the time that 
Unicron was trying to destroy Cybertron. I presumed them innocent, and had 
them killed. They turned this into an advantage and destroyed most of my 
Sharkticons. Then the ones known as the Dinobots came and turned my own 
Sharkticons against me! I fled, but it was to late, I was caught and nearly 
killed. Unicron, the Dark Master of all Quientessions, retrieved me. He, over 
time created the Destrons, desendants of the Quientessions. As a matter of 
fact, I do belive that the Tripredacus council was Destron, or as close as 
one could get. Do you understand now where I have been?"
